<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Document administratif</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: DejaVu Sans, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #0f1d35;
            font-size: 12.5px;
            line-height: 1.45;
            background: #f4f8ff;
        }

        .sheet {
            margin: 18px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #d8e4f6;
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #0a2f72, #1f5db7);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 22px 28px;
        }

        .hero-top {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .hero-top td {
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            width: 58px;
            height: 58px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95), rgba(222,234,255,0.72));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32);
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(8, 21, 51, 0.16);
            position: relative;
        }

        .brand-logo .logo-mark {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #123c8a;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .brand-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .brand-subtitle {
            margin: 4px 0 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(245, 250, 255, 0.92);
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .badge-demission { background: rgba(217, 70, 70, 0.24); }
        .badge-conge { background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.24); }

        .content {
            padding: 24px 28px 18px;
        }

        .meta {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #d6e2f4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .meta td {
            padding: 9px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5edf9;
        }

        .meta tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: 0;
        }

        .meta .label {
            width: 30%;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #18396e;
            background: #f3f7ff;
        }

        .section-title {
            margin: 16px 0 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #133364;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .box {
            border: 1px solid #d6e2f4;
            background: #fbfdff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
        }

        .reason {
            min-height: 150px;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }

        .timeline {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }

        .timeline td {
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding-right: 10px;
        }

        .mini {
            border: 1px solid #d6e2f4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .mini .k {
            font-size: 10.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            color: #60769b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .mini .v {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #15386f;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 28px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .signature .line {
            margin-top: 36px;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 230px;
            border-top: 1px solid #48618b;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 6px;
            color: #30486f;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 18px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5edf9;
            padding: 12px 0 2px;
            color: #60769b;
            font-size: 10.5px;
        }

        .qr-block {
            margin-top: 18px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .qr-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 128px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .qr-box img {
            width: 116px;
            height: 116px;
            display: block;
        }

        .qr-text {
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: middle;
            padding-left: 16px;
            color: #334155;
        }

        .qr-title {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #123c8a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sheet">
        <div class="hero">
            <table class="hero-top" role="presentation">
                <tr>
                    <td style="width:72px;">
                        <div class="brand-logo">
                            <div class="logo-mark">VOS</div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <h1 class="brand-title">Service Administratif - VOS</h1>
                        <p class="brand-subtitle">Document officiel genere le {{ submittedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="text-align:right; width:170px;">
                        <span class="badge {{ formData.request_type == 'demission' ? 'badge-demission' : 'badge-conge' }}">
                            {{ formData.request_type == 'demission' ? 'DEMISSION' : 'CONGE' }}
                        </span>
                        <div style="font-size:11px;margin-top:10px;opacity:0.92;">Ref: {{ reference }}</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <table class="meta" role="presentation">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Nom complet</td>
                    <td>{{ formData.full_name }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Email professionnel</td>
                    <td>{{ formData.email }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Poste</td>
                    <td>{{ formData.position }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Departement</td>
                    <td>{{ formData.department is not empty ? formData.department : '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table class="timeline" role="presentation">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="mini">
                            <div class="k">Date de debut / effet</div>
                            <div class="v">{{ formData.start_date|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="mini">
                            <div class="k">Date de fin</div>
                            <div class="v">
                                {% if formData.request_type == 'conge' and formData.end_date is not empty %}
                                    {{ formData.end_date|date('d/m/Y') }}
                                {% else %}
                                    N/A
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="section-title">Objet</div>
            <div class="box">
                {{ formData.request_type == 'demission' ? 'Notification de demission' : 'Demande de conge' }}
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">Motif / details</div>
            <div class="box reason">{{ formData.reason }}</div>

            <div class="signature">
                <div>Fait le {{ submittedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                <div class="line">Signature du demandeur</div>
            </div>

            <div class="qr-block">
                <div class="qr-box">
                    <img src="{{ qr_code_data_uri(qrPayload) }}" alt="QR code de verification">
                </div>
                <div class="qr-text">
                    <p class="qr-title">Verification rapide</p>
                    <div>Scannez ce QR code pour telecharger directement le PDF depuis votre telephone.</div>
                    <div style="margin-top:6px;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;">Reference: {{ reference }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                Ce document a ete genere automatiquement depuis le backoffice VOS.<br>
                Reference interne: {{ reference }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
